akan mengerti.

112
00:09:22,477 --> 00:09:23,477
Kau hebat.

113
00:09:25,437 --> 00:09:27,057
Kau juga akan semakin baik.

114
00:09:30,187 --> 00:09:31,357
Kau punya rencana besok?

115
00:09:32,147 --> 00:09:33,147
Besok?

116
00:09:33,567 --> 00:09:35,657
Aku seharusnya bertemu
Jay Jun besok sore.

117
00:09:35,737 --> 00:09:38,447
Akan bagus jika kalian berdua
menjadi dekat sebelum rekaman.

118
00:09:40,197 --> 00:09:42,907
Jika kau luang, bergabunglah
makan malam bersama kami.

119
00:09:45,707 --> 00:09:46,707
