dihamili temanmu?

145
00:10:52,897 --> 00:10:54,147
Lee Eun-Soo.

146
00:10:54,727 --> 00:10:55,857
Pertama, kau menyewa kamar.

147
00:10:56,737 --> 00:11:00,357
- Lalu mandi lebih bersih dari biasanya.
- Astaga.

148
00:11:00,447 --> 00:11:02,697
