181
00:13:33,267 --> 00:13:34,267
Astaga!

182
00:13:39,767 --> 00:13:40,817
Aku sudah tidak marah.

183
00:13:42,527 --> 00:13:43,817
Bagaimana denganmu?

184
00:13:53,247 --> 00:13:54,247
