00:17:37,597 --> 00:17:39,137
Kau akan pulang jam berapa?

225
00:17:39,217 --> 00:17:40,427
Apa?

226
00:17:42,517 --> 00:17:43,727
- Hari ini...
- Hari ini!

227
00:17:44,307 --> 00:17:45,437
Aku akan pulang larut.

228
00:17:45,767 --> 00:17:47,857
Sangat larut.
Aku ada makan malam dengan kolega.

229
00:17:48,057 --> 00:17:50,647
- Namun hari ini...
